The paper deals with the problem of binary classification of high dimensional data and introduces Bayesian models for the task. The paper also focuses on providing measures of uncertainty along with the classification. This makes it likely that the paper belongs to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Statistics (cs.ST), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
